<template>
        
                <form @submit.prevent="handleSubmit">
                <custom_input type="email" v-model="email"/>
                <custom_input type="password" v-model="password"/>
                <button>Log In</button>
    </form>


    </template>

    <script>
    import custom_input from "../components/CustomInputComp.vue"
    export default {
    name: "comp",
    components: ['custom_input'],
    data: function() {
        return {
            email: "",
            password: "",
            title: "Login Form"
        };
    },
    methods: {
        handleSubmit() {
            console.log(this.email, this.password)
        }
    }
    }
        
    </script>


    <style>

    input {
        margin: 10px;
        color:  blue;
        display: block;
    }

    </style>
